ComicInfo.Summary: Who is the new Backlash? Meanwhile, the feral hero Dingo is on the hunt for a fellow kindred, but there are others in these woods also hunting for Kindred, and Dingo just made their list. Plus, Backlash helps Quentin test the limits of his powers. This issue includes six handbook style dossiers including Backlash, Taboo, Crimson, Aries, Dingo, and Omni. Also includes a 2-page pin-up of Backlashs rogues gallery.
